<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1203037>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Caligus oviceps Shiino, 1952, female.A, habitus, dorsal; B, antenna, post-antennal process and maxillule drawn in situ; C, tip of maxilla; D, sternal furca; E, distal segment of exopod of leg 1; F, outer margin spines of exopod of leg 2; G, exopod of leg 3; H, leg 4. Scale bars:1.0 mm on A, 200 µmon B,H, 100 µm on C, D, F, G, 50 µm on E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1203037/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

